text:
How is it, wearing the new costumes?
How does it feel to have all the members together?

I feel like our unit,
is truly starting from here.

To live up to these costumes,
we have to keep polishing ourselves.

From now on, please continue to support us...
the "HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS."

Hm...?
Haha, what's wrong all of a sudden?

Sometimes, showing respect is important, right?
... Especially to important people.
